    <item>
      <title>[计算机网络] y</title>
      <link>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 00:00:00 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <author>xxx@example.com (byzh)</author>
      <guid>https://byzhrichard.github.io/post/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[计算机网络] y</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h1 id="常见问题">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%b8%b8%e8%a7%81%e9%97%ae%e9%a2%98"></a>
常见问题
</h1><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">无法访问
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">连接超时
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">无互联网连接
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">服务器无响应
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>本质是:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">1. DNS 问题：域名解析错了 / 解析不到
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">2. 路由问题：数据不知道该走哪条路
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">3. 代理问题：流量有没有走 Clash / VPN / 系统代理
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">4. 防火墙问题：被本机、服务器、路由器、防火墙拦了
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">5. 网关 / NAT 问题：内网出口转换出问题
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">6. 缓存问题：系统缓存了错误的解析或连接状态
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">7. 运营商问题：某些线路访问某些服务质量很差
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">8. 应用自身问题：Steam、浏览器、Git、pip、conda 各自有自己的网络策略
</span></span></code></pre></div>
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-05-29首发于<a href='https://byzhrichard.github.io/'>byzh的博客</a>，最后修改于2026-05-29</p>]]>
      </description>
      
        <category>计算机网络</category>
      
    </item>
    
    

    <item>
